# ai-choice choices configuration example
# Defines the classification options. Copy this file to choices.yaml and customize.
# This file contains application logic and can be version-controlled freely.

# Classification choices (at least one required)
# tag:         the value output to stdout when this choice is selected
# description: natural language description shown to the LLM for matching
choices:
  - tag: "weather"
    description: "天気予報や気象情報に関する質問や話題"
  - tag: "time"
    description: "現在時刻や時間の経過に関する質問や話題"
  - tag: "fortune"
    description: "占いや運勢、星座に関する質問や話題"
  - tag: "default"
    description: "上記のいずれにも当てはまらない質問や話題"
